description: Over 40 people who attended a Baptist service in Frankfurt after curbs were eased were infected.
title: Coronavirus: Over 40 Covid-19 cases traced to church service in Germany
title_page: Coronavirus: Over 40 Covid-19 cases traced to church service in Germany - BBC News
maintext: At least 16 of the people infected lived in Hanau, east of Frankfurt. As a result, the town has called off a prayer gathering that Muslim leaders had organised for this Sunday.
